name: The Deep Mask
description: This mask was spotted deep in the Pacific ocean around the Mariana Trench swimming amongst a swarm of jellyfish. At first it blended in, until it's unique patterns started to glow different colours catching the divers eye. On closer inspection it appeared to be some sort of mask for a cycloptic being constructed from living shellfish, anemones and sea kelp. The being that would wear such a thing is yet to be discovered.
